&lt;p&gt;The discharge lounge was created in November 2019 in order to create flow and support patients discharge from hospital. We are in a great position to continue this valuable service and now have an opportunity for a qualified Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit enthusiastic, motivated staff with excellent communication skills that have a passion for delivering kind and compassionate care. Recruiting motivated, capable and committed staff is the key to us maintaining our high standards of quality, safety and patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must have experience of delivering nursing care in an equivalent role within a health care providing organisation and be forward thinking, well organised with a positive attitude towards adaptability. Shortlisted applicants will be asked to attend a formal interview.&lt;/p&gt;
